title: Great views! 942sf 1BR apt, 17+ foot ceilings, Modern kitchen, has W/D
posting_body: ['Walk to theaters, fine restaurants, great Italian food, coffee shops, a vegan restaurant, nightclubs, a grocery store & deli, a drug store, museums and much more — all within two blocks!', 'Light rail and bus stops are just steps away.', 'Let the St. Claire Luxury Loft apartments be your San Jose apartment.', 'This apartment features:', 'Upscale interiors', 'Great views', '17+ foot ceilings and exposed brick walls', 'Restored 1930’s architectural details including original doors & hardware', 'Deluxe kitchens with stainless appliances, including microwave, dishwasher, and disposal', 'Convenient washer and dryer inside', 'Extra storage locker available', 'Come Visit us!', 'St Claire Apartments', '311 South 1st Street', 'San Jose, CA 95113', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday - Friday: 9:00 am - 6:00 pm', 'Saturday: 10:00 am - 4:00 pm', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', "related search terms ::: Downtown San Jose, Sudio, Above Original Joe's"]
